  "duration": 151.536,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 5.062,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, Jacob spake many more things to my people at that time;",
      "verse": "11:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 5.242,
      "end": 9.468,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless only these things have I caused to be written,",
      "verse": "11:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 9.648,
      "end": 12.992,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the things which I have written sufficeth me.",
      "verse": "11:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 13.672,
      "end": 21.195,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, write more of the words of Isaiah,",
      "verse": "11:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 21.375,
      "end": 23.79,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for my soul delighteth in his words.",
      "verse": "11:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 23.97,
      "end": 27.174,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For I will liken his words unto my people,",
      "verse": "11:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 27.354,
      "end": 31.023,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I will send them forth unto all my children,",
      "verse": "11:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 31.203,
      "end": 33.479,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he verily saw my Redeemer,",
      "verse": "11:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 33.659,
      "end": 35.284,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even as I have seen him.",
      "verse": "11:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 35.964,
      "end": 41.119,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And my brother, Jacob, also has seen him as I have seen him;",
      "verse": "11:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 41.299,
      "end": 45.339,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I will send their words forth unto my children",
      "verse": "11:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 45.519,
      "end": 49.141,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to prove unto them that my words are true.",
      "verse": "11:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 49.321,
      "end": 51.55,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, by the words of three,",
      "verse": "11:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 51.73,
      "end": 53.03,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "God hath said,",
      "verse": "11:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 53.21,
      "end": 54.882,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will establish my word.",
      "verse": "11:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 55.062,
      "end": 58.22,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nevertheless, God sendeth more witnesses,",
      "verse": "11:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 58.4,
      "end": 60.861,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he proveth all his words.",
      "verse": "11:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 61.541,
      "end": 66.278,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, my soul delighteth in proving unto my people",
      "verse": "11:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 66.458,
      "end": 68.919,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the truth of the coming of Christ;",
      "verse": "11:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 69.099,
      "end": 73.325,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for, for this end hath the law of Moses been given;",
      "verse": "11:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 73.505,
      "end": 76.756,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all things which have been given of God",
      "verse": "11:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 76.936,
      "end": 80.233,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the beginning of the world, unto man,",
      "verse": "11:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 80.413,
      "end": 81.992,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are the typifying of him.",
      "verse": "11:4",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 82.672,
      "end": 86.898,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And also my soul delighteth in the covenants of the Lord",
      "verse": "11:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 87.078,
      "end": 89.586,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he hath made to our fathers;",
      "verse": "11:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 89.766,
      "end": 92.97,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, my soul delighteth in his grace,",
      "verse": "11:5",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 93.15,
      "end": 97.097,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in his justice, and power, and mercy",
      "verse": "11:5",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 97.277,
      "end": 101.317,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in the great and eternal plan of deliverance from death.",
      "verse": "11:5",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 101.997,
      "end": 105.48,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And my soul delighteth in proving unto my people",
      "verse": "11:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 105.66,
      "end": 110.072,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that save Christ should come all men must perish.",
      "verse": "11:6",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 110.752,
      "end": 114.56,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For if there be no Christ there be no God;",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 114.74,
      "end": 117.108,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and if there be no God we are not,",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 117.288,
      "end": 119.749,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for there could have been no creation.",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 119.929,
      "end": 122.901,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But there is a God, and he is Christ,",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 123.081,
      "end": 126.75,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he cometh in the fulness of his own time.",
      "verse": "11:7",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 127.43,
      "end": 131.006,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I write some of the words of Isaiah,",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 131.186,
      "end": 140.567,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that whoso of my people shall see these words",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 140.747,
      "end": 144.369,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "may lift up their hearts and rejoice for all men.",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 144.549,
      "end": 146.267,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now these are the words,",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 146.447,
      "end": 150.859,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and ye may liken them unto you and unto all men.",
      "verse": "11:8",
      "lineIndex": 41
    }
  ]
}